{"tid":2151060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地爆買蘋果其實就係同共產黨打緊一場資訊戰","createTime":"2020-08-11T08:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T11:56:57.000Z","uid":266286,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"613ae1e2b6291095ebbe45da2896d1bcabfb5bb9","tid":2151060,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"重點從來都唔係話要比錢蘋果賺<br />\n而係要令成件事有關注度<br />\n要吸引關注就要發生啲平時唔會發生既事<br />\n否則想表達既訊息亦都唔會傳到各位耳中<br />\n<br />\n既然拉人封艇係為左滅聲<br />\n咁就要用更有關注度既方法去對抗<br />\n令到被滅既聲更響更亮<br />\n咁先可以令到佢做左既野 負面影響力減到最低<br />\n<br />\n我地控制唔到共產黨唔拉人<br />\n但係我地可以將佢做既野 對自己利益最大化<br />\n<br />\n成日話香港人抗爭有創意<br />\n其實創意既價值就係依到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買蘋果買蘋果買蘋果"},{"pid":"2da96dce94b7a08a1284fe45cbe3d25a043199cb","tid":2151060,"uid":266286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"終於有得同共產黨打仗<br />\n唔係輸下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1aeb480bda957b2e25ef79b941bcc932d0b840","tid":2151060,"uid":16775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"除左政治版 財經版都make到d noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7c4706cbc9fb0724b4424f23b88cad0e258443","tid":2151060,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a1aeb480bda957b2e25ef79b941bcc932d0b840","tid":2151060,"uid":16775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"除左政治版 財經版都make到d noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"無錯 只需要一部電話 㩒一粒制 就可以立即同共產黨開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dee2a108b38997608ffb65d7cfe5c46f78a425c","tid":2151060,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},